Show fleet nodes, service assignments, and service health, derived from object storage

Usage: sleet status [OPTIONS] --spec <SPEC>

Options:
      --spec <SPEC>
          Path to the fleet spec TOML file

      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format

          Possible values:
          - text: Human-readable text
          - json: JSON matching the subcommand's response schema
          
          [default: text]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
